            This sample showcases the features in SfMultiColumnDropDownControl. SfMultiColumnDropDownControl is a selection control with drop down SfDataGrid that can be shown or hidden by clicking the arrow control. It provides textbox to the user. Based on the user input, it shows the possible suggestion to the users. The SfMultiColumnDropDownControl provides features like AllowAutoComplete, AllowIncrementalFiltering, AllowCaseSensitiveFiltering, AllowImmediatePouup and ReadOnly.

